  tech: `<svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="8" y="8" width="32" height="32" rx="4"/><path d="M16 20l4 4-4 4M24 28h8"/></svg>`,
